{"tid":401814,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"用咗一個月外A酸, 皮膚好咗好多","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T07:07:09.000Z","uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb281184fa6cbd9d6300c7bc0a5bd729821836be","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"講返本來皮膚係點先<br />\n我唔係勁爛面, 但毛孔好大, 成日出油<br />\n同埋成日生大大粒石頭瘡 仲好多暗粒<br />\n<br />\n用咗一個多月<br />\n皮膚明顯好咗, 少咗生石頭瘡, 皮膚滑咗同白咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過毛孔仲係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 油都有繼續出<br />\n<br />\n我用果支係differin 0.1% , 係第3代A酸 比第一代冇咁刺激<br />\n但我之前已經成日用酸, 果酸,杏仁酸,水楊酸等等。所以用differin 都冇敏感過, 但冇用過既巴絲最好小心d用。"},{"pid":"156dd8488ce45afb46bf57298a43cc9ef5aef3d9","tid":401814,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"differin 0.1%算係弱定勁？"},{"pid":"b7d8a1c3c8e841fbe91238fbb95b0cc3a541e0bd","tid":401814,"uid":5850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打知道用咩先可以將D 毛孔收返細呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 毛孔越黎越粗大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216b72d7e6c22ce5cf3bbbf3f91715e569f96fff","tid":401814,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"有冇前後比較圖"},{"pid":"4cec597b9e89b818680b4ea83a4ad26a14fdd8a2","tid":401814,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"點買？"},{"pid":"339a5ef386d2648c9d74d975e961b18ff67709ee","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>differin 0.1%算係弱定勁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係超熟A酸, 但應該係弱。第一代勁d, <br />\n例如Rentin-A. 但刺激性比較大, 我上網見過有人(可能用錯), 用到皮膚爛, 所以我都唔亂敢。"},{"pid":"275ea8f33a542b9e80c7bc7ffb7f3406e324589f","tid":401814,"uid":17610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:49:53.000Z","msg":"係邊買？"},{"pid":"4c47c7a7f55885f19bc1a364058a8465c61de12a","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我起旺角買 唔洗醫生紙。$140左"},{"pid":"44506be785d52f5d4d69a5423fe283cb5e386093","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇前後比較圖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry 冇點影相. 但因為我本來唔係好嚴重 睇相分別唔大"},{"pid":"4934380f9c4523cd4717271ac8ef831648c0bea0","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴絲打知道用咩先可以將D 毛孔收返細呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 毛孔越黎越粗大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毛孔大好樣衰, 成日好驚同人近距離講野"},{"pid":"899908e92808cdb62d752d66feaff5f15167e5da","tid":401814,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我起旺角買 唔洗醫生紙。$140左</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以影個盒睇吓？thx"},{"pid":"5ca12aa68c396727bc719ba6d3f2567d8b9a043c","tid":401814,"uid":142686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"邊度有得買 我同樓主情況差唔多"},{"pid":"f0868dc53189526abb0edcf7093b8d630e421e64","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我起旺角買 唔洗醫生紙。$140左</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以影個盒睇吓？thx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/I47Pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FI47Pw&d=2eCDVJIknrktphmt0Xw3Uv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=91730b7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/a/I47Pw</a>"},{"pid":"bfd5c88954b61b7b84a990b981bea2712b7c6c7c","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度有得買 我同樓主情況差唔多</blockquote><br />\n旺角d藥房應該都有"},{"pid":"d2f8060c280d45ce781dbeae846bf1571c15b964","tid":401814,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊度有得買 我同樓主情況差唔多</blockquote><br />\n旺角d藥房應該都有</blockquote><br />\n點用 洗面定點?"},{"pid":"d291883b5e07e502e2bb3bc54a7a74633126272a","tid":401814,"uid":114900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊度有得買 我同樓主情況差唔多</blockquote><br />\n旺角d藥房應該都有</blockquote><br />\n點用 洗面定點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜晚洗完面之後搽面<br />\n記得用少少就夠 1~2粒豆咁多<br />\n薄薄地咁就ok<br />\n之後等30分鐘左右又上返d保濕<br />\n如果第一次用 最好局部揸少少睇下有冇敏感先"},{"pid":"2385ff880239554e9b5bc88806fb3bf502b10820","tid":401814,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:40:42.000Z","msg":"收細毛孔好似要做機，普通搽護膚品唔會收到，但好似成效都係麻麻地"},{"pid":"c0cc87047ac3d447850caafe6526bb78957bbfac","tid":401814,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收細毛孔好似要做機，普通搽護膚品唔會收到，但好似成效都係麻麻地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\na酸唔係護膚品黎"},{"pid":"7423d78fa2214fa469bb7a12010edeba17ebeec2","tid":401814,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收細毛孔好似要做機，普通搽護膚品唔會收到，但好似成效都係麻麻地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\na酸唔係護膚品黎</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n但a酸收到毛孔？"},{"pid":"5fd78a44d067ce575c0d92c61917056e06bfd1f3","tid":401814,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:49:55.000Z","msg":"始終建議跟醫生指示<br />\n<br />\n不過要用既話要慢慢build up tolerance, 等皮膚慢慢適應, 初初1星期1次，詳情做下功課。脫皮乾燥都係比較正常既反應，揀返啲修復既乳/霜配合使用。"},{"pid":"dcb33a8453d1e74b7e21eceeafc10b4535a1f2aa","tid":401814,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:39:06.000Z","msg":"毛孔係要激光先得<br />\n搵皮膚科醫生"},{"pid":"7aa9867cc361a532e472061037b8752c5dfe119b","tid":401814,"uid":71053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"番大陸醫院開便好多<br />\n一樣法國出"},{"pid":"c6d6c5f2e38bfcfdba591784e86c7d8ac3034934","tid":401814,"uid":71205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"用開0.3 冇曬角質會滑啲"}]}